# Data Governance

- Store runtime outputs under `KHUKRA_DATA_ROOT`; do not write generated files outside governed zones.
- Preserve DuckDB catalog and Parquet/JSON file consistency when adding writes or deletes.
- Record lineage and version metadata for data-producing workflows where existing services support it.
- Treat model artifacts as governed metadata unless real binary artifact storage is explicitly designed.
- Add audit/workflow records for user-triggered actions that change shared state, or document the gap.
- Update `docs/data-governance.md` when adding storage zones, retention behavior, or lifecycle semantics.
